@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sucpyg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(v2))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin(0.27))
    tmp = 0.19
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.18) * (tmp + 0.88 - v2 + 0.40)) + v0)
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
